    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When a creature hits as a result of your Spotter's Order they deal extra damage equal to your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1) and you can expend a Merit die to place it on the target as if through your Strike like Iron. You must have a Merit die available to be placed in this way.</p><p>Additionally, the following effects are among your Exploit options:</p><p><strong>Anvil Strike.</strong> If the Warlord whose Merit Die triggered this Exploit is adjacent to the creature being targeted, they may make an Unarmed Strike against the creature (no action required). This Unarmed Strike can be used to Shove, Grapple, or deal damage.</p>",
